    <note>Fan(2) Zhongwen [7214] Fan(2) Yu [3290], a Youzhou (Gaoping jun) resident and the fourth generation ancestor of Zhongwen, his younger brother, Zhongyan [8043] and their lineage cousin, Qi [3273] (Shidao's [581] father), held office in Suzhou at the end of the Tang and remained as a resident of Wuxian. Zhongwen was Chunren's [559], Chunli's [560] and Chuncui's [561] uncle, Shen(2) Chong's [7321] and Zhou(1) Shihou's [7198] father-in-law. Suzhou FZ, 76.29a; Fan Zhongyan. WJ, 13.24a-25b. CBD, 2, 1653.</note>
